title: Check IP SLA instances on Cisco devices
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/cisco
author: Ralf Ertzinger <re at addix.net>
license: GPL
distribution: addon
description:
 This check monitors IP SLA monitoring instances on Cisco
 devices. Currently only SLA instances of type icmp-echo
 are supported.

 Depending on the state of the SLA monitor the checks can
 be {OK}, {CRIT} or {UNKNOWN}.

item:
 The IP SLA id as configured on the Cisco device

inventory:
 One check for each configured SLA of type icmp-echo is created
 by the inventory.
